-- Spain's Mapfre buys Italian, German arms of Direct Line for 550 mln eur 
-- By Paul Day
-- Thu Sep 25, 2014 02:15AM EDT
-- None



MADRID, Sept 25 (Reuters) - Spanish insurance company Mapfre <MAP.MC> said on Thursday it had acquired the Italian and German affiliates of UK-based general insurer Direct Line <DLGD.L> for 550 million euros (702.19 million US dollar).

